n style=\"color: rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 11px; text-align: justify;\">December 2016: Thank you for 150 schools! &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Ubuntu, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<u><a href=\"https://links.clevermonitor.com/?c=8a003276-e6a4-5ea4-adb3-cea661ae195a&e=jeeproject%40yahoo.com&t=camp&r=8bd9f5582028ad68bf781891a17e2da5\" target=\"_blank\">View this email in your browser</a></u></span></font></p><p></p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr> \n \n </div></table><table class=\"cm-cb-sections\" id=\"emailBody\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><tr><td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" class=\"flexibleContainer\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"600\" class=\"flexibleContainerCell\" background=\"\" bgcolor=\"\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" class=\"flexibleContainerBox\" style=\"padding-top:0px;padding-right:20px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:20px;\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\" align=\"center\" class=\"imageContent\"><div style=\"width:560px;\"><a href=\"https://links.clevermonitor.com/?c=8a003276-e6a4-5ea4-adb3-cea661ae195a&e=jeeproject%40yahoo.com&t=camp&r=2f3d0e080de0f8e0b822eb5d93a79113\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://content.static.clevermonitor.com/3/368/2016-12-16_3411770505/0dfa396e00a61f6a6bf8ea84d373f12b.png\" width=\"600\" style=\"max-width:100%;display:block;\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" moz-do-not-send=\"true\"></a></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n \n \n </td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr>\n \n <tr><td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" class=\"flexibleContainer\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"600\" class=\"flexibleContainerCell\" background=\"\" bgcolor=\"\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" class=\"flexibleContainerBox\" style=\"padding-top:20px;padding-right:20px;padding-bottom:5px;padding-left:20px;\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\" class=\"textContent\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><p><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\"><font face=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\"><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 59); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;\">Dear Friends,</span></font></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\"><font face=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\"><br style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 59); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;\"></font></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\"><font face=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\"><br style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 59); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;\"></font></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\"><font face=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\"><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 59); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;\">As the end of 2016 approaches, we want to thank you for being a part of the Happy Hearts Fund family and reflect on what we've accomplished together!</span></font></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\"><font face=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\"><br style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 59); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;\"></font></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\"><font face=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\"><br style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 59); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;\"></font></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\"><font face=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\"><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 59); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;\">This year, you helped Happy Hearts Fund reach a huge milestone:&nbsp;</span></font></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\"><font face=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 59); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;\">150 schools</strong></font></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\"><font face=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\"><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 59); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;\">. That means that&nbsp;</span></font></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\"><font face=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 59); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;\">74,000 children</strong></font></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\"><font face=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\"><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 59); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;in ten countries around the world can now access their human right to education. We are overjoyed with how much we've done together since our founding ten years ago.</span></font></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\"><font face=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\"><br style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 59); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;\"></font></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\"><font face=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\"><br style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 59); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;\"></font></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\"><font face=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\"><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 59); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;\">While we celebrate this achievement with you, we're faced with the ever-present reminder that more children around the world are waiting to get back to school following natural disasters.</span></font></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\"><font face=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\"><br style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 59); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;\"></font></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\"><font face=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\"><br style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 59); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;\"></font></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\"><font face=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\"><a href=\"https://links.clevermonitor.com/?c=8a003276-e6a4-5ea4-adb3-cea661ae195a&e=jeeproject%40yahoo.com&t=camp&r=2f3d0e080de0f8e0b822eb5d93a79113\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: 100%; color: rgb(41, 169, 219); font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline; font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">This holiday season, a generous partner will match every donation, doubling your gift.</a></font></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\"><font face=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\"><br style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 59); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;\"></font></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\"><font face=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\"><br style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 59); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;\"></font></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\"><font face=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\"><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 59); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;\">Thanks to Lexington Partners, your gift will be matched dollar for dollar up to $30,000.&nbsp;Take advantage of this incredible opportunity\u2014stand with children once more before the close of 2016 and have your contribution matched.</span></font></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\"><font face=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\"><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 55, 59); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;\"><